                            img.img-fluid.d-block.mx-auto(src='assets/img/portfolio/app-detontator.png', alt='...')
                            p Single page application project to detonate app binary to provide source code level details including app author, signature and build information using React and Go. https://appdetonator.run/
                            a 
                            ul.list-inline
                                li
                                    strong Client:
                                    | AppDetonator
                                li
                                    strong Category:
